headline: This Canadian Electronics Stock Keeps Surging On AI Spend
summary: Canadian electronics manufacturer Celestica kept rising Wednesday after an exceptional earnings report earlier this week.  On Wednesday Celestica stock jumped 3.5%.  In the third quarter, it outperformed analyst expectations across the board.

headline: CLS Gains Traction in the AI Data Center Market: Will it Persist?
summary: CLS surges as its AI data center business becomes the company's fastest-growing segment, fueled by soaring demand for high-performance compute infrastructure.
